{"tid":1612823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"親子活動 - 油漆汽球畫","createTime":"2019-10-02T11:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T02:46:36.000Z","uid":187050,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"53291cdeeaf6f5fbb01571f0b7eb002036ebaf47","tid":1612823,"uid":187050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:08:12.000Z","msg":"大家呢幾個月精神應該比較緊張，今日我地用藝術放鬆下<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n油漆汽球點整：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1WhwqkaVGXM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D1WhwqkaVGXM&d=zBKsoIV%2FeLhWSsP5H2J%2BmolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=4cd92e67\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1WhwqkaVGXM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有咩咁好玩：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cH1WAHu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcH1WAHu.png&h=119ab44b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n制成品：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LK9pKyK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLK9pKyK.png&h=2024fd16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n安全提示：<br />\n請勿向人掉，就算人地有頭盔甚至盾牌，都會令人忽然失去視野，好危險的，唔好試<br />\n請勿向車頭玻璃掉，輕則架車清潔好前唔可以再開，重則炒車，好大獲的，唔好試"},{"pid":"e6be9b8a40d4cacd8d31cbc3c73ba6411c4ba22d","tid":1612823,"uid":114347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:09:33.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b21f014f6313fe4ad3a6550439adc82842e7a9","tid":1612823,"uid":187050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:13:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"675d91fa8e44b40d27ecfca2462af3eefd59fdbc","tid":1612823,"uid":75364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T11:14:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"caf37cdf4783187d7cce4c7c00511ca1dd766fad","tid":1612823,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-